  m_text: Now that you have selected an attack, move your mouse over to the ogre
    to set it as a target. All avaliable targets in range are highlighted as shown.
    If you change your mind on which unit to select when there are multiple later,
    you can press the esc key to deselect the targets or any units. esc key also
    brings up the pause menu. Once the target is set, press end turn to carry out
    the attack.
