  m_text: Now if you have been paying attention you would have seen an ogre slowly
    making its way across the screen. It is now your job to deal with him in combat.
    Move your unit close to it until u see the attack phase pop up on the top right,
    click on the warrior to set its attacks. The warrior's range is low so get close!
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
